300
00:45:18,183 --> 00:45:19,932
Just us.

301
00:45:32,307 --> 00:45:33,308
Tiku.

302
00:45:41,058 --> 00:45:42,057
Manu.

303
00:45:48,683 --> 00:45:49,725
S.T.

304
00:45:54,974 --> 00:45:55,973
Nano.

305
00:46:32,390 --> 00:46:33,224
I see something.

306
00:46:33,433 --> 00:46:34,433
