656
01:41:38,516 --> 01:41:39,933
until the train leaves.

657
01:41:40,516 --> 01:41:41,932
Only fourteen minutes?

658
01:41:56,267 --> 01:41:58,100
You'd better get going.

659
01:42:01,183 --> 01:42:03,515
